_sText:
Gg_texturedcity_atk_v2, not made by me, made by my friend stone. A new dev style city with multiple buildings many windows, doors, ladders. Everything you love about textured cities. Plenty of room for each type of gun and holes in roofs for dropping down on unsuspecting foes. The whole city is easily maneuverable and the city is the correct size for a gun game.
other: im not sure on the maximum players, but 32 is a guess. dedicated to the atk clan.
